Bill O'Reilly - love him hate him he is not a Democrat nor a hardcore Republican (his views might be the same but he is not blind)  Actually watch his show some time and see who he criticizes ... more often its the Republicans although he has a special dislike for hippiesque people who are living in the 60's.<br>
