As for the rest of the posters who are speaking about the problems with invading North Korea (I personally think they don't want any part of it and thats why they admitted it).  No it wouldn't just be airstrikes.  But the technology of the US Armed Services is far beyond what our closest allies have.  Britain and other nations were amazed at what we did in Afghanistan (technically not that we did it) and the enourmous leap in technology from the Gulf War til now.  Don't fool yourself into thinking that a war would be so difficult.  <br>
